quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  33,41,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU EDHKURU ELLAHE DHIKRÆN KETHIRÆN
  33,42,WE SEBBIHUHU BUKRETEN WE ‘ESILÆN
  33,43,HUWEL-LEDHI JUSELLI ‘ALEJKUM WE MELA’IKETUHU LIJUHRIXHEKUM MINE EDH-DHULUMATI ‘ILA EN-NURI WE KANE BIL-MU’UMININE REHIMÆN
  33,44,TEHIJETUHUM JEWME JELKAWNEHU SELAMUN WE ‘E’ADDE LEHUM ‘EXHRÆN KERIMÆN
  33,45,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU ‘INNA ‘ERSELNAKE SHAHIDÆN WE MUBESHSHIRÆN WE NEDHIRÆN
  33,46,WE DA’IÆN ‘ILA ELLAHI BI’IDHNIHI WE SIRAXHÆN MUNIRÆN
  33,47,WE BESHSHIRIL-MU’UMININE BI’ENNE LEHUM MINEL-LAHI FEDLÆN KEBIRÆN
  33,48,WE LA TUTI’IL-KAFIRINE WEL-MUNAFIKINE WE DA’ ‘EDHAHUM WE TEWEKKEL ‘ALA ELLAHI WE KEFA BILLAHI WE KILÆN
  33,49,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA NEKEHTUMUL-MU’UMINATI THUMME TELLEKTUMUHUNNE MIN KABLI ‘EN TEMESSUHUNNE FEMA LEKUM ‘ALEJHINNE MIN ‘IDDETIN TA’TEDDUNEHA FEMETTI’UHUNNE WE SERRIHUHUNNE SERAHÆN XHEMILÆN
  33,50,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU ‘INNA ‘EHLELNA LEKE ‘EZWAXHEKEL-LATI ‘ATEJTE ‘UXHUREHUNNE WE MA MELEKET JEMINUKE MIMMA ‘EFA’EL-LAHU ‘ALEJKE WE BENATI ‘AMMIKE WE BENATI ‘AMMATIKE WE BENATI HALIKE WE BENATI HALATIKEL-LATI HAXHERNE ME’AKE WE EMRE’ETEN MU’UMINETEN ‘IN W
  33,51,TURXHI MEN TESHA’U MINHUNNE WE TU’UWI ‘ILEJKE MEN TESHA’U WE MENI EBTEGAJTE MIMMEN ‘AZELTE FELA XHUNAHE ‘ALEJKE DHALIKE ‘EDNA ‘EN TEKARRE ‘A’JUNUHUNNE WE LA JEHZENNE WE JERDEJNE BIMA ‘ATEJTEHUNNE KULLUHUNNE WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU MA FI KULUBIKUM WE KANEL-LAHU ‘
  33,52,LA JEHILLU LEKE EN-NISA’ MIN BA’DU WE LA ‘EN TEBEDDELE BIHINNE MIN ‘EZWAXHIN WE LEW ‘A’XHEBEKE HUSNUHUNNE ‘ILLA MA MELEKET JEMINUKE WE KANEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN REKIBÆN